title: 135 candidates: What happened the last time California recalled a governor
description: As the recall campaign against California Governor Gavin Newsom takes a step closer, Carrie Dann looks at what happened in 2003 when a recall election replaced Gray Davis with Arnold Schwarzenegger.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
